{
  "stem": "3855.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're sending us to Bremen to be shipped out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the doors finally opened, it was on a pleasant countryside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were asked to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Younger people jumped out happily.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Older people climbed out as best as they could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we formed a marching column.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then marched into this magnificent, filigreed, iron gate. 'Arbeit macht frei,' 'work will make you free.' And we were assembled on this huge campground.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there, in the middle of this campground, was something like a chair.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- I'm stressing this because this is important.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And here they took this one fellow that they had standing on the side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they announced-- and they must have had loudspeakers by then because a lot of the announcements were on the speaker.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This gentleman was found with several false passports in his possession.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He has to be punished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They announced it like this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They strapped him over this torture chair.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And two guys took turns beating him mercilessly until he collapsed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As I think back, there was a purpose to this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was to imbue in us the thought of terror.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is what can happen to you if you don't kowtow, if you don't behave, if you do anything wrong.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this was just a demonstration.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a simple device, an object lesson-- object, they say, an object-- to make us realize this is not a summer camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If you don't behave, forget it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's how it worked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were put into different buildings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Dachau was new then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Everything was immaculate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Our washroom was immaculate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The building had wooden bunks with straw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I slept on a lower one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We used to have two, three guys in each bunk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was about this wide.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
